resoFacts.basement: Finished, Bath Full, Exterior Entry, Storage Space, Interior Entry, Utility Room, Laundry Facilities

data.description: Must see beautiful well maintained 3 bedroom and 2 full baths ranch style home. Updated kitchen. Freshly painted. Hardwood floors throughout the home. Stainless steel appliances with a fully finished basement. New condenser. Completely private fenced in yard with plenty of space. Near parks with easy access to all major highways, shopping centers, and restaurants. Showings start 4/28/2022. Home inspection limited to environmental/structural. "AGENT RELATED TO SELLER". Best and final offer by 5/3/22 5 pm.
